snippet.title: HIRAETH Trailer (RPG Maker Horror Adventure Game)
snippet.description:
Hiraeth is out now! Free to play, made in RPG Maker with over 1000 work hours from two lifelong friends and gamers. A unique adventure horror game full of surrealism, dream worlds, animal friends, and loads of lore. Download on itch.io for free and play now!

https://tpetrichor.itch.io/hiraeth
